{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% set is_privacy = doc == 'privacy' %}
{% block title %}{{ is_privacy ? 'Privacy Policy' : 'Terms of Service' }} | Evec Tours{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<section class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">
        <header class="legal-header">
            <span class="legal-badge">{{ is_privacy ? '🔒 Privacy' : '📄 Legal' }}</span>
            <h1>{{ is_privacy ? 'Privacy Policy' : 'Terms of Service' }}</h1>
            <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>
        </header>

        <div class="legal-body">
            {% if is_privacy %}
                <p>At <strong>Evec Tours</strong> we respect your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights. <em>(This is a starting template — replace the text below with your final policy.)</em></p>

                <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
                <p>When you create an account, make a reservation, or contact us, we may collect your name, email address, phone number, and travel preferences. We also collect basic usage data (pages viewed, searches) to improve our service.</p>

                <h2>2. How we use your information</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>To process and manage your bookings and payments.</li>
                    <li>To send booking confirmations, reset emails, and important updates.</li>
                    <li>To respond to your enquiries and provide customer support.</li>
                    <li>To improve our website, offers, and recommendations.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>3. Sharing</h2>
                <p>We do not sell your personal data. We share it only with trusted providers needed to deliver our service (e.g. payment processors, email and hosting providers), and where required by law.</p>

                <h2>4. Data security</h2>
                <p>We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data. No method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, but we work to keep your information safe.</p>

                <h2>5. Your rights</h2>
                <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting us. You can also delete your account from your profile settings.</p>

                <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
                <p>We use essential cookies to keep you signed in and remember your preferences (such as currency). You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

                <h2>7. Contact</h2>
                <p>For any privacy questions, email us at <a href="mailto:contact@evectours.com">contact@evectours.com</a>.</p>
            {% else %}
                <p>Welcome to <strong>Evec Tours</strong>. By using our website and services, you agree to these terms. <em>(This is a starting template — replace the text below with your final terms.)</em></p>

                <h2>1. Using our service</h2>
                <p>You must be at least 18 years old (or have parental consent) to make a booking. You agree to provide accurate information and to use the service lawfully.</p>

                <h2>2. Bookings & payments</h2>
                <p>All bookings are subject to availability and confirmation. Prices are shown in the selected currency and may change until a booking is confirmed. Payment must be completed through our approved payment methods.</p>

                <h2>3. Cancellations & refunds</h2>
                <p>Cancellation and refund conditions depend on the specific voyage or offer and any third-party suppliers involved. Refund requests are reviewed on a case-by-case basis as described at the time of booking.</p>

                <h2>4. Responsibilities</h2>
                <p>You are responsible for ensuring you hold valid travel documents (passport, visas, insurance) for your trip. Evec Tours acts as an organizer and is not liable for events outside our reasonable control.</p>

                <h2>5. Intellectual property</h2>
                <p>All content on this site (text, images, logos) belongs to Evec Tours or its licensors and may not be reused without permission.</p>

                <h2>6. Changes to these terms</h2>
                <p>We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the service after changes means you accept the updated terms.</p>

                <h2>7. Contact</h2>
                <p>Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:contact@evectours.com">contact@evectours.com</a>.</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.legal-page { padding: 60px 20px 80px; background: var(--dark-bg, #0a0f1c); min-height: 60vh; }
.legal-container { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; background: var(--amazon-white, #111d33); border: 1px solid var(--border-dark, #1e3050); border-radius: 20px; padding: 48px; }
.legal-header { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dark, #1e3050); padding-bottom: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.legal-badge { display: inline-block; background: rgba(245,195,0,.12); color: var(--amazon-orange, #f5c300); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.legal-header h1 { color: var(--text-primary, #e5e7eb); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 8px; }
.legal-updated { color: var(--text-muted, #8fa3c0); font-size: .85rem; margin: 0; }
.legal-body { color: var(--text-muted, #8fa3c0); line-height: 1.75; font-size: .96rem; }
.legal-body h2 { color: var(--text-primary, #e5e7eb); font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 28px 0 10px; }
.legal-body p { margin: 0 0 14px; }
.legal-body ul { margin: 0 0 14px; padding-left: 22px; }
.legal-body li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
.legal-body a { color: var(--amazon-orange, #f5c300); text-decoration: none; }
.legal-body a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .legal-container { padding: 28px 20px; } }
</style>
{% endblock %}
